				.d-flex
					.img-fluid
						img(src=`${CWD}assets/img/gallery/layer.png` alt='...')(style='height:30px; width:30px')
					.ml-3
						h5.mb-3
							| Start your project with us
						p.text-muted.mb-4.mb-md-0
							| Our work doesn't end with the making of excellent products. We continue to thrive by helping our clients.
